#~ "a precursor to supervised tasks."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "They introduced <b>contrastive divergence</b> "
#~ "and <b>greedy layer-wise training</b>, "
#~ "which remain valuable tools in the "
#~ "generative modeling toolkit."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "They inspired subsequent generative models,"
#~ " including <b>Variational Autoencoders (VAEs)</b>"
